          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/by Authors/.The Decay Curves were Resolved Cleanly",
                "Into Three Components, 32-Min Cs-138, 2.9-Hr Cs-134-M a",
                " 12.9-Day Cs-136, with a Long-Lived, Low-Activity Tail.",
                "The Gamma-Spectrum of this Sample Revealed Two Photo-",
                "Peaks Attributable to Cs-134-G (2.1-YR) And Cs-137",
                " (30-YR) After the Decay of Cs-136. Both the Cs-134-M",
                "And the Cs-134-G Activities were Measured Relative to",
                "That of Cs-136 from the B- And Gamma-Ray Measurements",
                "Respectively. The Independent Yield of Cs-134-G was",
                "Obtained by Difference Between the Two Measurements."
              ]
            }
